码在运行中, in[]数组、out[]数组、temp[]数组、gindex、lindex、result会分别存在GPU硬件哪个存储层次, 并简单解释。</p><p><br/></p><p>__global__&nbsp;void&nbsp;stencil_1d&nbsp;(int&nbsp;*in,&nbsp;int&nbsp;*out)&nbsp;{<br/><br/><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;__shared__&nbsp;int&nbsp;temp[_SIZE&nbsp;+&nbsp;2&nbsp;*&nbsp;RADIUS];&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;int&nbsp;gindex&nbsp;=&nbsp;threadIdx.x&nbsp;+&nbsp;blockIdx.x&nbsp;*&nbsp;blockDim.x;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;int&nbsp;lindex&nbsp;=&nbsp;threadIdx.x&nbsp;+&nbsp;RADIUS;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;temp[]&nbsp;=&nbsp;in[];<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(threadIdx.x&nbsp;&lt;&nbsp;RADIUS)&nbsp;{<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;temp[lindex&nbsp;-&nbsp;RADIUS]&nbsp;=&nbsp;in[gindex&nbsp;-&nbsp;RADIUS];<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;temp[lindex&nbsp;+&nbsp;BLOCK_]&nbsp;=&nbsp;in[gindex&nbsp;+&nbsp;BLOCK_];&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;//Apply&nbsp;the&nbsp;stencil&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;int&nbsp;result&nbsp;=&nbsp;0;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;for&nbsp;(int&nbsp;offset&nbsp;=&nbsp;-RADIUS&nbsp;;&nbsp;offset&nbsp;&lt;=&nbsp;RADIUS&nbsp;;&nbsp;offset++)&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;result&nbsp;+=&nbsp;temp[lindex&nbsp;+&nbsp;offset];<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;Store&nbsp;the&nbsp;result<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;out[gindex]&nbsp;=&nbsp;result;<br/>}<br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>","Type":"ShortAnswer","data":{},"Score":3,"index":0,"score":3,"Answer":"","Remark":"","isEdit":true,"Options":[],"Version":"b9406c9ef80a48559d80b873e89917f9","TypeText":"主观题","HasRemark":false,"LibraryID":9710,"max_retry":1,"TemplateID":804370,"difficulty":1,"library_id":9710,"problem_id":6805,"ProblemType":5,"template_id":804370,"AllowResults":["text","pic","file"],"review_detail":{}},{"Body":"<p>下面哪种不属于分布式系统中的直接互连网络类型<br/></p>","Type":"SingleChoice","data":{},"Score":0.5,"index":0,"score":0.5,"Answer":["D"],"Remark":"","isEdit":true,"Options":[{"key":"B","value":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;\">环面网格</span></p>"},{"key":"D","value":"<p><span style=\"font-fam